OL,3,GYorkshire & Humber
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FShowers
OL,6,Ffading into the evening, with some
OL,7,Fclear spells likely. Low cloud, mist
OL,8,Fand some light rain or drizzle then
OL,9,Fspreading inland from the North Sea.
OL,10,FMilder than recent nights.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTuesday:FCloudy start with outbreaks
OL,13,Fof light rain or drizzle, although
OL,14,Fthese easing by the afternoon. Cooler
OL,15,Fthan recently, especially in the
OL,16,Fonshore breeze, but turning sunny from
OL,17,Fthe east later.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
