OL,3,GYorkshire & Humber
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:
OL,6,FOvernight cloud and mist clearing
OL,7,Fearly Wednesday and Thursday to give
OL,8,Fsome warm sunshine, but tempered by
OL,9,Fstrong onshore breezes. Sunny spells
OL,10,Fand lighter winds Friday, but perhaps
OL,11,Falso showers.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
